metadata.name: NIRVANA: DAY
metadata.description:
Here in Nirvana, art thrives. Freedom of Expression is the only thing that continues to matter. it is the only place where she can truly express herself by doing the one thing she loves , CREATING.

Here in Nirvana, she's home. A space where she's free, where her imagination runs wild and is able to roam freely without any limitations. A place without rules or expectations.
